title: Living Sacrifice Discography 1989-2010 (11 Releases)
description:
----------------------------------------------------------------
LIVING SACRIFICE DISCOGRAPHY
----------------------------------------------------------------

This Living Sacrifice discography may or may not be complete.  It includes the following 11 releases...

 * 1989 - Not Yielding To Ungodly - Demo
 * 1991 - Living Sacrifice
 * 1992 - Nonexistent
 * 1994 - Inhabit
 * 1997 - Reborn
 * 2000 - The Hammering Process
 * 2002 - Conceived In Fire
 * 2005 - In Memoriam
 * 2008 - Death Machine
 * 2009 - Overkill Exposure - Single
 * 2010 - The Infinite Order

Living Sacrifice is a Christian heavy metal band that formed in September 1989 in Little Rock, Arkansas.

God Bless,
TorrentTracts - November 2012
